Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,椿感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.67,0:00:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一年有一半穿裤子的女猩猩感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.04,0:00:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪的喷嚏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,生化危机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,卫生兵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,退避
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.52,0:00:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,大猩猩毒菌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.89,0:00:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,说谁是猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.64,0:00:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,大猩猩杀过来啦
