Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,给你  柠檬水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,感冒了要补充维C  妈妈说的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我又没感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.67,0:00:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,猩猩也不会感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,椿又不是猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,椿是女生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:00:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,治好了
